
                 Sentence Splitter
                 -----------------

This directory contains a sentence splitter, copied over from the
moses-smt project (Moses Statistical Machine Translation).  This 
splitter and its data files are covered according to the LGPLv2.1
(Lesser GNU Public License Version 2.1)

The sentence splitter is here for only one purpose: to support
the language-learning project, which, at this time, usese RelEx
only indirectly.  In particular, this sentence splitter is NOT
used by any other part of RelEx at this time (2013/2014).
